{{Infobox protected area | name = Natural Areas of the Llobregat Delta | alt_name = Espais Naturals del Delta del Llobregat {{ca icon}} | iucn_category = | photo = Semafor.jpg | photo_alt = | photo_caption = A [[bird hide]] for [[birdwatching]] | photo_width = | map = Spain Catalonia | map_alt = | map_caption = Location of the delta in [[Catalonia]] | map_width = | location = [[Province of Barcelona]], [[Catalonia]], [[Spain]] | nearest_city = | coords = {{coord|41|18|10|N|2|7|55|E|region:ES-CT|format=dms|display=inline,title}} | coords_ref = | area = 923 ha | established = | visitation_num = | visitation_year = | governing_body = [[Generalitat de Catalunya]] | world_heritage_site = | url = http://www.deltallobregat.cat/?lang=en }} The '''Llobregat Delta''' ({{lang-ca|Delta del Llobregat}}) is the [[River delta|delta]] of the [[Llobregat]] river, located near the city of [[Barcelona]], [[Catalonia]], northeastern [[Spain]]. The current delta has been altered by [[Agriculture|farming]], [[urban planning|urban development]], [[industrialisation]] and transport [[infrastructure]]s such as the [[Port of Barcelona]] and the [[Barcelona El Prat Airport]].
==The Natural Areas of the Llobregat Delta== The Natural Areas of the Llobregat Delta ({{lang-ca|Espais Naturals del Delta del Llobregat}}) is a network of [[protected area]]s established in 1987 that belongs to the [[municipality|municipalities]] of [[El Prat de Llobregat]], [[Viladecans]], [[Gavà]] and [[Sant Boi de Llobregat]]. It encompasses more than 900 hectares over the right margin of the river that have been declared a [[Special Protection Area]] as a designation under the [[European Union]] [[Birds Directive|Directive on the Conservation of Wild Birds]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deltallobregat.cat/?url=espais_naturals_en|title=The Delta, Natural areas |author= |date= |work=Consortium of the Natural Areas of Delta del Llobregat |publisher=deltallobregat.cat |accessdate=February 4, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deltallobregat.cat/?url=delta_llobregat_en|title=The Llobregat delta |author= |date= |work=Consortium of the Natural Areas of Delta del Llobregat |publisher=deltallobregat.cat |accessdate=February 4, 2012}}</ref>
