je]] |18400 |- |[[Prolom Banja]] |18433 |- |[[Provo (Vladimirci)|Provo]] |15215 |- |[[Pružatovac]] |11413 |- |[[Pukovac]] |18255 |- |[[Putinci]] |22404 |}
